
QuantumPay Mainnet Declaration v1.1

(Signed & Checksummed Release)

Document Version: v1.1
Network: QuantumPay Mainnet
Chain ID: 77001
Status: ✅ FINAL & FROZEN
Declaration Date: 16 January 2026


1. Declaration

This document formally declares the readiness and activation status of the QuantumPay Mainnet.

QuantumPay is a resilient digital payment and settlement network designed to operate reliably under normal conditions and predefined crisis scenarios, including infrastructure disruptions.

As of the declaration date above:

The QuantumPay Mainnet is operational

The Chain ID 77001 is permanently frozen

Core consensus, block production, and network stability have passed extended soak testing

No further breaking protocol changes are planned prior to public mainnet usage


2. Chain ID Finalization

Chain Name: QuantumPay Mainnet

Chain ID: 77001

Policy:

> The Chain ID 77001 is permanently frozen and MUST NOT be changed under any circumstances.

Changing the Chain ID after this declaration would:

Break wallet compatibility

Invalidate signatures and historical transactions

Fragment the network and tooling ecosystem


3. Network State Summary

Continuous block production: ✅

Multi-node deployment: ✅

Snapshot & recovery procedures: ✅

Crisis Mode operational doctrine: ✅

Mainnet documentation published: ✅


The network is considered stable for ecosystem integration, including wallets, explorers, and external services.


4. Cryptographic Attestation

This declaration is cryptographically bound to its content via checksum.

SHA-256 Checksum (Document v1.1):

<TO_BE_FILLED_AFTER_FINAL_SAVE>

> The checksum must be generated from the final committed file content
Example command:



sha256sum MAINNET_DECLARATION_v1.1.md

Any modification to this document after publication invalidates this checksum.


5. Governance & Finality

This declaration represents a final governance statement for the QuantumPay Mainnet launch phase.

Subsequent changes, if any, must be issued as:

New declaration versions, or

Addendum documents explicitly referencing this declaration


6. Closing Statement

QuantumPay Mainnet is declared LIVE, FINAL, and GOVERNANCE-FROZEN with respect to its Chain ID and core protocol identity.

This declaration serves as a public, auditable, and verifiable reference for the global community.


QuantumPay Core Team
